# Berezovka, Blagoveshchensky District, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Berezovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Tugaysky Selsoviet, Blagoveshchensky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 12 as of 2010. There are 2 streets.
Geography
Berezovka is located 65 km northeast of Blagoveshchensk (the district's administrative centre) by road.
